64044c14aba09f","tid":1839821,"uid":272196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqL49xL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqL49xL.jpg&h=84ade640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工會要人！<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線昨日呼籲政府，必須於一月二十八日前全面落實香港邊境防疫措施，否則將不排除會行動升級，包括發動工業行動！<br />\n<br />\n請各醫管局員工透過以下 google form 連結 (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/36LfYF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36LfYF4&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77YleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=594a1cf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36LfYF4</a>)，從速加入工會，壯大工會聲勢，讓工會可持有最強而有力的談判權！<br />\n<br />\n請各市民分享此 post，邀請身邊的醫管局員工加入工會！<br />\n<br />\n政府無能，港人自救！"},{"pid":"55d02b0b32007da06fe0b6b1a9f89c1b73cce107","tid":1839821,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"好多錯字"},{"pid":"8a513b2e108f80d0a32f6a27fa5d0ed6bb2900bf","tid":1839821,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"政府唔閉關<br />\n醫護遲早都係會病到七七八八<br />\n咁同早啲罷工有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n希望你會罷工<br />\n不過尊重你既決定<br />\n萬事小心"},{"pid":"0a1ff03895a25173f63b7c0bbbd66d8fed286ead","tid":1839821,"uid":76877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"個ac好乾淨wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e124baa120569863666955413e069574f5a8d22","tid":1839821,"uid":181080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"死咗點報仇<br />\n有d野唔係非黑即白<br />\n有冇諗到非常時期做道德撚其實係最唔道德"},{"pid":"0f055be663e121e39a926f4799ac0a5b2404fe56","tid":1839821,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"無證你寫乜都得"},{"pid":"a17e6cd5b506ccb3a86901ccca2175bc8c9503b7","tid":1839821,"uid":156579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"睇下武漢醫生段片<br />\n唔好睇到自